quran[148]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"Mi fu…ó…óorii innde Allah jon yurmeende huu…ìunde juul…ìe e heefer…ìe fow ka aduno, jooma yurmeende hertornde jul…ìe …ìen tun ka laakara"
  1,2,Yettoore nden ko Allah jooma tageefu On woodani
  1,3,Jooma yurmeende hu…ìtidinnde e heeriinde
  1,4,Jooma √±alngu njo…ìdiiji
  1,5,Ko Aan tan min ndewata te ko Aan tan min mballintoo
  1,6,Feewnu min e laawol pooccingol
  1,7,Laawol ngol …ìeen …ìe neemin-…óaa …ìe ngonaa tikkanaa…ìe te …ìe majjaani
  2,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  2,2,"Ndeen deftere sikke alaa he mayre, ko nde peewal wonande hul…ìe …ìe"
  2,3,∆Åeen goon…óinoo…ìe mbirniindi e…ìe √±ii…ìna juulde e…ìe nafga e ko Min nje…ói …ìe
  2,4,"E …ìeen goon…óinoo…ìe ko Min njippini dow maa e ko jippinaa ado ma, e…ìe njananaa √±alaande wattan"
  2,5,"∆Åeen dey ngoni ko e peewal iwngal e Joomii …ìe, ko kam…ìe ngoni da…óoo…ìe"
  2,6,"∆Åeen yeddu…ìe ngoon…óintaa foti a jeertinii …ìe wolla a jeertinaani, fof foti e mum en"
  2,7,"Alla muppi …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe, wirngallo woni noppi e gite ma…ì…ìe lette maw…óe na woodani …ìe"
  2,8,"Na woodi heen yim…ìe wi'oo…ìe min ngoon…óinii Alla e √±alaande wattan, tawa …ìe ngoon…óinaani"
  2,9,"E…ìe koda Alla e goon…óin…ìe …ìe, alaa mbo …ìe kodata sonaa ko'e ma…ì…ìe tawa …ìe nganndaa"
  2,10,Ko √±awo woni e …ìer…óe Alla …ìeydani …ìe √±awu maa lette muus…óe njan e mum en sabu ko …ìe pennannoo
  2,11,So …ìe mbi'aama taa bonnee e lesdi ndi …ìe mbi'a minen ko min mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe
  2,12,Ko kam…ìe tigi ngoni bonnoo…ìe kono …ìe tinataa …óum
  2,13,"So …ìe mbi'aama ngoon…óinee wano yim…ìe …ìee ngoon…óiri, …ìe mbi'a mbela minen ngoon…óina wano …óaay…ìe …ìee ngoon…óiniri, kono ko kam…ìe tigi ngoni …óaay…ìe kono …ìe nganndaa"
  2,14,"So tawii …ìe kawrii e goon…óin…ìe …ìe mbi'a: min ngoon…óinii, so …ìe njeewdii e sey…óanooji ma…ì…ìe …ói …ìe mbi'a: minen ko onon min ngonndi min njalkitat tan"
  2,15,Alla jalkita …ìe O …ìeydana …ìe bewre …ìe ngona e wemmbere
  2,16,"Ko …ìeen ngoni soodir…ìe peewal majjere njeeygu ma…ì…ìe alaa tono, te …ìe peewaano"
  2,17,∆Åe nanndi ko e ku…ì…ìu…óo jayngol nde ngol yaynii Alla nawi ooyre ma…ì…ìe O acci …ìe e ni…ìe …ìe nji'ataa hay huunde
  2,18,Ko fah…óu…ìe muum…óu…ìe wum…ìe …ìe nduttotaako
  2,19,Wolla wano to…ìo iwde asamaan na woodi ni…ìe e digaali e maje …ìe cukka noppi ma…ì…ìe sabu kartaali (par√±ite) ngam reentaade maayde Alla noon Ombo hi…ìindii ge…óe heefer…ìe
  2,20,"Majal ngal na …óe…ìa yulde gite ma…ì…ìe kala nde ngal yaynii …ìe njaha heen so ni…ì…ìi…óii …ìe ndaroo, so Alla welano nawa nan…óe e gite ma…ì…ìe sabu Alla ko kattan…óo kala huunde"
  2,21,Onon yim…ìe ndewee Jooma mon tag…óo on tagi adii…ìe on mbela joo kulon Alla
  2,22,"Oon mba…óan…óo on lesdi ndi mbertu O wa…ói Asamaan o mahoodi tii…óndi O jippini ndiyam iwde e Asamaan O yaltini heen …ìi…ì…ìe le…ó…óe woni nje…óu mon, taa mba…óanee Alla nanndidii…ìe te o…óon nganndi goonga o"
  2,23,"So tawii o…óon cikkitii e Kur'aana mbo Min njippini dow jeyaa…óo Amen o, ngaddee simoore nanndunde hembo, nodde wallidii…ìe mon gaa Alla so tawii o…óon ngoon…ói e nodditaandu mon ndu"
  2,24,"So tawii on mba…óaani …óum -te on mbaawataa …óum- kulee jayngol ku…ì…ìirtengol yim…ìe e kaa∆¥e, ngol heblanaa ko heefer…ìe …ìe"
  2,25,"Weltin …ìeen goon…óin…ìe …ìe ngolli mo∆¥∆¥i wonde …ìe…ì ke…ìa aljannaaji caalli na ndonga les majji kala nde …ìe nje…óaa toon …ìi…ì…ìe le…ó…óe …ìe mbi'a ko …óee min nje…óanoo ko adii, kono si …ìe mee…óii …óe …ìe tawa e…óe ceerti, e…ìe ke…ìa toon rew…ìe laa…ì…ìe …ìe √±ii…ìida toon. @Corrected"
  2,26,"Alla aamantaa addude yeru hay so wonii wano …ìowngu e ko …ìuri …óum, so tawii ko goon…óin…ìe e…ìe nganndi ko goonga iw…óo e Jooma ma…ì…ìe, so tawii ko yeddu…ìe …ìe mbi'a holko Alla yi…ói e oo yeru Ombo majjina heew…ìe O feewna heen heew…ìe, alaa majjintee…óo heen sonaa yaltu…ìe …óoftaare. @Corrected"
  2,27,∆Åeen firtoo…ìe aadi Alla …ìaawo tii…óneede mbo e…ìe ta∆¥a ko Alla yamiri yo jokke e…ìe mbonna ka lesdi ko kam…ìe ngoni rus…ìii…ìe (pertu…ìe)
  2,28,Holno njeddirton Alla tawa ngoodaano O wuurni on rewa heen O wara on rewa heen O wuurtina on …ìaawo …óuum ko e Makko nduttoto-…óon
  2,29,Kanko tagani on kala ko woni e lesdi ndi …ìaawo …óuum O faandii asamaan O fotndi mbo asamaanji jee…ói…ói Kanko ganndu…óo kala huunde. @Corrected
  2,30,"Nde Joom maa wi'i malayka en maa Mi wa…ó lomto Am e lesdi ndi, …ìe mbi'i mbela wa…óat heen bonnoowo dufoowo ∆¥ii∆¥e tawa minen ko Aan tan min njettata mi…óen Ma teddina, O wi'i Miin Mi…óo anndi ko on nganndaa"
  2,31,"O anndini Aadama in…óe …óe fofo, rewi heen O holli …óe malaykaa…ìe …ìe O wi'i kaalanee Kam in…óe …ìee …óoo so tawii o…óon ngoon…ói"
  2,32,∆Åe mbi'i senaande woodanii Ma alaa ko min nganndi sonaa ko nganndin-∆äaa min ko Aan tan woni ganndid…óo kala huunde √±ee√±…óu…óo
  2,33,O wi'i aan Aadama anndin …ìe in…óe majji nde o anndini …ìe in…óe …óee O wi'i mbela Mi wi'aano on Miin Mi…óo anndi mbirniindi asamanji e lesdi Mi…óo anndi ko pe√±√±inton e ko cuu…óoton fof
  2,34,Nde Min mbii malaykaa…ìe …ìe cujjanee Aadama …ìe cujji sonaa Ibliisa o salii o mawnikinii ndeen o jeyaa e yeddu…ìe
  2,35,Min mbii aan Aadama yah ho…óoy aljanna aan e debbo maa √±aamee toon ko welata on kala …óo mbela-…óon taa …ìado-…óee kii lekki ndeen on jeyete e too√±…ìe
  2,36,Sey…óaane hoomti …ìe haa yaltini …ìe e mo∆¥∆¥ere nde …ìe ngonndoo Min mbii …ìe njippo-…óee ngonon a√±ondir…ìe ke…ìon √±ii…ìal dow lesdi ndi e dakmitaare haa happu yonta
  2,37,Aadama he…ìi konngi iwde e Joom mum O accani mo ko Kanko woni jaafotoo…óo jurmotoo…óo
  2,38,Min mbi'i njippo-…óee toon onon fof so tawii Mi addii e mon peewal kala dew…óo peewam Am …ìeen dey kulol alanaa …ìe kadi …ìe cunotaako
  2,39,∆Åeen yeddu…ìe penni maandeeji Amen ko …ìeen ngoni yim…ìe jayngol ko toon …ìe √±ii…ìata
  2,40,Onon …ìi…ì…ìe Isra'iil ciftoree mo∆¥∆¥ere Am nde Mi wa…óani on njottinee aadi Am Mi yottina aadi mon te kulon Kam Miin tan
  2,41,"Ngoon…óinee ko njippin-Mi na goon…óini ko njogi-…óon ko taa ngonee adii…ìe yeddude …óum wota on eto soodirde aayeeje am …óe coggu hoyngu, kulee kam Miin tan"
  2,42,Taa jii…ìindiree goonga e fenaande o…óon cuu…óa goonga o tawa o…óon nganndi mbo
  2,43,√ëii…ìnee juulde tottiron asakal …óigganon njankinano-…óon Alla
  2,44,"Mbela on njamirat yim…ìe …óiggere njejjiton ko'e mon tawa o…óon njanga deftere nde, mbela on kakkilantaa …óum"
  2,45,"Mballitoree mu√±al e juulde, pellet honde sa…ótani dow mbo yankinii…ìe …ìe"
  2,46,∆Åeen yananaa…ìe maa kawru e joom ma…ì…ìe ko he Makko …ìe nduttotoo
  2,47,"Onon …ìi…ì…ìe Isra'iil ciftoree neemaaji Am …ói neemin MI mon, ko Miin tigi …ìurni e dow winndre he"
  2,48,Kulee √±ande fittaandu alaa ko waawani fittandu wonndu ndu ja…ìantaake tefangol go…ó…óo coodtiigu kadi ja…ìetaake …ìe ke…ìataa ballo
  2,49,"Tuma Min ndanndii on yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìe mba…óii on lette bon…óe …ìe kirsa …ìi…ì…ìe mon …ìe ngoppa rew…ìe mon nguura, ina e …óuum lette maw…óe iwde ga Jooma mon"
  2,50,Nde Min peccani on maayo ngo Min ndanndi on Min njooli yim…ìe Fir'awna o…óon ndaarda gite mon ≈ãaas
  2,51,Nde Min podani Muusaa jammaaji capan…óe nayi fawii heen ndew-…óon ngaari ndi caggal Am onon ko on too√±oo…ìe
  2,52,Fawii heen Min ngaccani on …ìaawo …óuum mbela joo njetton
  2,53,Nde Min ngaddani Muusa deftere nde e Furgaana mbela joo peewon
  2,54,Nde Muusaa wi'i yim…ìe makko onon yim…ìe am on too√±ii ko'e mon nde ndew-…óon ngaari ndi ndutto…óee e tag…óo on o mbarto-…óon …óuum …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ande on to Jooma mon O accana on Kanko woni gaccanoowo njurmotoo…óo
  2,55,Nde mbii-…óon Muusaa min ngoon…óitaa haa min nji'a Alla ko laa…ìi ndeen hartaango (jayngol iwde asamaan) …ìami on o…óon ndaarda gite mon
  2,56,Fawii heen Min nguurtini on …ìaawo nde maay-…óon mbela joo njetton
  2,57,"Min …óuwdini on duule Min njippinani on njuumri dakmundi e colli ju…óaa…ói √±aamee e bel…ói ko Min nje…ói on, wonaa Minen …ìe too√±i ko ko'e ma…ì…ìe …ìe too√±atnoo"
  2,58,Min mbii naatee ndee saare √±aamon heen ko mbela-…óon mbeltoron naatee damal ngal o…óon njankinii mbi'on accan min ndeen Min njaafoo on goopi mon Min …ìeydana mo∆¥∆¥in…ìe …ìee mo∆¥∆¥ereeji
  2,59,Too√±…ìe …ìee mbayliti konngol ngol …ìe mbi'anoo ndeen Min njippini dow too√±oo…ìe …ìee lette sabu ko …ìe ngonno ko faasqeebe
  2,60,"Nde Muusaa toranii yim…ìe mum ndiyam Min mbi'i fiyu haayre nde sawru maa ndu ndeen gite ndiyam sappo e …ói…ói puccitii heen yim…ìe …ìee fof ke…ìi yarde, √±aamee njaree e nje…óu Alla taa mba…óee bonannde dow lesdi ndi"
  2,61,"Nde mbii-…óon aan Muusaa min min njondintaako e √±aamdu wooturu torano min Joom maa O yaltinana min pu…ói lesdi gila e kappe e haakooji e buudi e √±ebbe e basalle (jabaa) mayri o, wi'i mbela on nji…ó lomtinde ko ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude ko, ke…ìon ko …ìuri jaasde …óuum njippo-…óee Misara maa on ke…ì ko tori-…óon ko …ìe pawaa koyeera e woro…óde …ìe nduttorii e tikkere Alla sabu …ìe njedduno aayeeje e…ìe mbara Annabaa…ìe ko aldaa e goonga …óuum noon ko goopi e too√±e ma…ì…ìe"
  2,62,"∆Åeen goon…óin…ìe e…ì…ìen feew…ìe e nasaara en e …ìe ngalaa diine,kala goon…óin…óo Alla e √±alaande wattan o golli ko mo∆¥∆¥i …ìeen ke…ìata njo…ìdi to Jooma ma…ì…ìe kulol alanaa …ìe te kam…ìe …ìe cunotaako"
  2,63,Nde Min …ìami aadi mon Min ummini fello Tuur dow mon ∆¥ettee ko Min ngddani on e semmbe ciftoree ko woni heen mbela joo kulon Alla
  2,64,Fawii heen caggal …óuum ndu≈ãti-…óon taw naano …ìural Alla e yurmeende Makko dow mon maa on njeye e bonnoraa…ìe
  2,65,On nganndii …ìeen too√±…ìe e mon √±ande hoore-biir (samdi) Min mbii …ìe ngontee baa…ói booraa…ói
  2,66,Min mba…ói …óum woni maande teskuye wonande …ìe e aroyoo…ìe e tinndinoore wonande hul…ìe Alla …ìe
  2,67,"Muusaa wi'i yim…ìe makko Alla yamirii on nde kirsoton nagge …ìe mbii mbela nanngir-…óaa min ko …óaay…ìe? o wi'i: mi…óo moolii Alla jeyeede e majju…ìe"
  2,68,"∆Åe mbii du'ano min Jooma maa O la…ì…ìinana min no nge wa'i. O wii: ko nge wonaa nayeye wonaa √±alel ko hakindiinge mba…óee ko njamira-…óon ko"
  2,69,"∆Åe mbii torano min Jooma maa O la…ì…ìinana min ngoobu (kulor) magge ? O wii: Oon wii ko sooye no feewi enge weli laarde"
  2,70,∆Åe mbii du'ano min Joom maa O la…ì…ìinana min no nge wa'i sabu na'i …ói nanndiri min maa min njiitu nge
  2,71,"O wi'i Kanko dee O wii ko nagge ne'iraange golle remru ngesa, kono wonaa yarnude gese, ko hisnge nge jillaani, …ìe mbii jooni dey a addii goonga …ìe kirsi nge kono …ìe …óe…ìaani wa…óde yamiroore nde"
  2,72,Nde mbar-…óon fettaandu ngon-…óon e tuumondirde ko Alla yaltini ko cuu…óno-…óon
  2,73,Min mbii tappindiree …ói ko noon Alla wuurtinirta maay…ìe O holla on kaawase Makko mbela joo kakkilon
  2,74,"Fawii heen …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óe njoori …ìaawo …óuum …óe mba'i no kaa∆¥e maa …ìura noon, sabu kaa∆¥e na ngoodi jaltinooje caalli go…ó…óe na peecoo njaltina ndiyam go…ó…óe kadi njowtoo janansabu hulde Alla, Alla noo yeebotaako ko ngolloton ko"
  2,75,Mbela o…óon …óaminii maa …ìe ngoon…óinan on tawa na woodi e ma…ì…ìe sete nanoowo haala Alla …ìe mbaylita ka caggal nde …ìe paami …ìe nganndi ka
  2,76,"So …ìe kawri e goon…óin…ìe …ìee …ìe mbii min ngoon…óinii so …ìe njeewdii …ìe mbi'a mbela on kaalanat …ìe ko Alla udditani on, ndeen …ìe ka…ìora on …óum to Jooma mon, mbela on kakkilantaa"
  2,77,Mbela …ìe nganndataa wonde Alla Mbo anndi ko …ìe cuu…óta e ko …ìe …ìa≈ãnginta
  2,78,"Na woodi e mum en humambinnee…ìe …ìe nganndaa e deftere nde sonaa janngugol penaale …óe …ìe nganndinaa, …ìe ngoni e sikkude tan"
  2,79,"Bone woodanii …ìeen winndiroo…ìe deftere nde juu…óe ma…ì…ìe e…ìe mbi'a …óum ko to Alla iwri haa …ìe coodira nde coggu hoyngu, bone wonan …ìe e ko juu…óe ma…ì…ìe mbinndi e kala ko …ìe paggitii heen"
  2,80,∆Åe mbii jayngol memataa min sinaa bal…óe see…óa wii …ìe mbela on ke…ìii fodoore Alla te Alla luutndotaako aadi Makko wolla ngon-…óon ko haalde e Alla ko on nganndanaa
  2,81,"Ko goonga kala mbo faggitii bonannde bon…ói makko piilii mo, ko …ìeen ngoni yim…ìe jayngol luttoo…ìe toon"
  2,82,∆Åeen goon…óin…ìe …ìe ngolli mo∆¥∆¥ereeji ko …ìeen ngoni yim…ìe aljanna luttoo…ìe toon
  2,83,Min …ìamii fodoore e …ìi…ì…ìe Isra'iil taa ndewee sonaa Alla mo∆¥∆¥on e jibnaa…ìe e jiidaa…ìe e waay…óu…ìe e waas…ìe o…óon kaalana yim…ìe …ìe ko mo∆¥∆¥i darnon juulde tottiron asakal …ìaawo …óuum cali-…óon …óuurni-…óon sonaa see…óa e moo…óon
  2,84,Nde Min ∆¥etti fodoore mon wota on nduf ∆¥ii∆¥e mon taa on njaltin ko'e mon galleeji mon …ói ndeen nja…ì-…óon ceedi…óon …óum
  2,85,"Rewi heen onon …ìee o…óon mbara ko'e mon o…óon njaltina yim…ìe e mon galleeji ma…ì…ìe, o…óon pe√±√±ina too√±e mon e ma…ì…ìe, si …ìe arii e mon dahaa…ìe coodtidon…ìe yaltingol …ìe na harmi e mon, mbela on goon…óinat yoga e deftere nde njeddon yoga heen kala e mon wa…óoo…ìe …óum njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ko koyeera weejo aduna √±ande darnga …ìe nduttee e lette …ìur…óe bonde Alla noon yeebotaako ko ngolloton ko"
  2,86,∆Åeen soodir…ìe laakara nguurndam aduna …ìe koynantaake lette …ìe ke…ìataa ballo
  2,87,Min ngaddanii Muusaa deftere nde …ìaawo makko Min ndewni heen nulaa…ìe Min ngaddani Iisaa …ìii Maryam la…ì…ìinale Min cemmbirini mo wonki tedduki mbela kala nde nulaa…óo addi he mon ko welaani pittaali mon mawnikino-…óon yoga heen njeddon …ìe yoga heen mbaron …ìe
  2,88,"∆Åe mbii …ìer…óe amen …óe ko uddii…óe, accu tan ko Alla hu…ói …ìe sabu keefeeru ma…ì…ìe, na fam…ói ko …ìe ngoon…óinta"
  2,89,"Nde deftere ari e ma…ì…ìe iwde e Alla, ende nuun…óina ko …ìe njogii ado …óuum …ìe ngonndoo ko wallitoraade …óum dow …ìeen yeddu…ìe nde ko …ìe nganndi ko ari he ma…ì…ìe …ìe njiddi …óum, yo ku…ódi Alla won e heefer…ìe"
  2,90,Bone woni e ko…ìe coodiri ko'e ma…ì…ìe nde …ìe njeddi -e too√±e- ko Alla jippini Alla jippinta …ìural Makko dow mbo O welaa e jeyaa…ìe Mako …ìe kaandii e tikkere mawnde heefer…ìe …ìee na ke…ìa lette bon…óe
  2,91,"Si …ìe mbi'aama ngoon…óinee ko Alla jippini ko …ìe mbi'a min ngoon…óina ko jippinaa e amen …ìe njedda ko wonaa …óuum te ko …óuum woni goonga nuun…óin…óo ko …ìe njogii, wii …ìe ko wa…ói o…óon mbarannoo annabaa…ìe Alla …ìe so tawno o…óon ngoon…óini"
  2,92,Nde Muusaa addani on la…ì…ìinale njogiti-…óon ngaari ndi …ìaawo makko onon ko on too√±oo…ìe
  2,93,"Min …ìami e mon fodoore Min …ìamti dow mon haayre Tuur ∆¥ettiree ko Min ngaddani on ko e semmbe nanee, …ìe mbii min nanii min ngoopi …ìer…óe mum en …óe keewi dak rewde ngaari ndi e keefeeru ma…ì…ìe, wii bone wonii e ko goon…óingol mon yamiri on so tawno o…óon ngoon…óini"
  2,94,Wii so tawii ko onon tan ke…ìata aljanna to laakara njelo…óee maayde so tawii ko on goon…óu…ìe
  2,95,∆Åe njelotaako …óum pooma e ko juu…óe ma…ì…ìe ngardini Alla Ombo anndi too√±oo…ìe …ìe
  2,96,Maa a taw ko kam…ìe …ìuri reer…óude e nguurndam e …ìeen renndin…ìe e Alla mbela gooto e ma…ì…ìe na yi…ói wuurde duu…ìe ujunere wuurde mbo ko juuti wo…ó…óintaa mo lette Alla Mo yi'a golle ma…ì…ìe
  2,97,Wii kala gon…óo ga√±o Jibriil yo anndu ko kanko yottini Kur'aana nder …ìernde maa e yamiroore Alla nde nuun…óini defte …óe …ìe njogii ko nde peewal e malu goon…óin…ìe
  2,98,Kala gon…óo ga√±o Alla e malaykaa…ìe Makko e nulaa…ìe Makko e Jibriil e Miika'il Alla dey ko ga√±o heefer…ìe …ìe
  2,99,Min njippinii e maa maandeeji la…ì…ìinooji alaa jeddoowo …ói sonaa faasigee…ìe …ìe
  2,100,Wolla kala nde …ìe pi…ìi aadi wooda e ma…ì…ìe firtu…ìe mbo accu tan …ìur…ìe heewde e ma…ì…ìe ngoon…óinaani
